overview.en: Turing Chain is the world's first put forward the concept of ABI,Using blockchain technology to solve artificial intelligence knowledge graph construction and verification,And open third-party interface to facilitate other developers to quickly build their own industry AI applications and hardware equipment public chain.
overview.zh: 图灵链（Turing Chain）是全球首个提出ABI理念、用区块链技术解决人工智能知识图谱搭建和校验，并开放第三方接口方便其他开发者迅速搭建自己行业的AI应用及硬件设备的公链。
